ds.name: TweeBot® HandsFree Bluetooth® Device
ds.txtjj: The totally hands-free TweeBot device easily pairs with your smartphone, then becomes your personal assistant! Just tell her to read a text "send an email" even post on Facebook! And best of all, you can do it completely HANDS FREE with simple voice commands! So when your hands are busy driving, cooking or working, just let TweeBot dial, text, read email, post or tweet!

ds.name: Wonder Cap
ds.txtjj:
Is your hair damaged from chemical colouring and use of hair straighteners? Do you want to have your own deep conditioning treatment at home? Now you can every week in the comfort of your own bathroom with the revolutionary Wondercap. The heat from your microwavable WonderCap opens up the hair cuticles allowing the conditioning treatment to nourish and replace moisture to the inner hair shaft. Use WonderCap with your favourite hair conditioner.

ds1.name: Mrs. Stick -Twiggy 11"
ds1.txtjj: Safer than a real stick and a whole lot more fun! The Stick Family have been designed for dogs who love to play and fetch real sticks but these sticks don't cause nasty mouth injuries like splinters, cracked teeth and damaged gums.

ds1.name: Octopus Shaped Docking Speaker
ds1.txtjj: iPods and iPhones rise from the head of adorable octopus as your favorite tunes pulse with 10 watts of sound and a 4" bass active woofer. Devices charge as they dock beside LED power and volume indicators. Docks also feature a 3.5 mm input jack that connects to smartphones, stereo systems, and DVD players, allowing you to enjoy Wilhelm screams with the utmost clarity.
